{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_019ZNFZeL7rhGkDVF2mvJSgm","type":"tool_result","content":"{\"issues\":{\"totalCount\":2,\"nodes\":[{\"expand\":\"renderedFields,names,schema,operations,editmeta,changelog,versionedRepresentations\",\"id\":\"12502\",\"self\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/rest/api/3/issue/12502\",\"key\":\"KATA-894\",\"fields\":{\"summary\":\"GetCasEventMediaPresignedUrls\",\"issuetype\":{\"self\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/rest/api/3/issuetype/10005\",\"id\":\"10005\",\"description\":\"A small, distinct piece of work.\",\"iconUrl\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/rest/api/2/universal_avatar/view/type/issuetype/avatar/10318?size=medium\",\"name\":\"Task\",\"subtask\":false,\"avatarId\":10318,\"hierarchyLevel\":0},\"created\":\"2025-10-17T14:55:37.536-0700\",\"project\":{\"self\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/rest/api/3/project/10001\",\"id\":\"10001\",\"key\":\"KATA\",\"name\":\"Katana\",\"projectTypeKey\":\"software\",\"simplified\":false,\"avatarUrls\":{\"48x48\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/rest/api/3/universal_avatar/view/type/project/avatar/10413\",\"24x24\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/rest/api/3/universal_avatar/view/type/project/avatar/10413?size=small\",\"16x16\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/rest/api/3/universal_avatar/view/type/project/avatar/10413?size=xsmall\",\"32x32\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/rest/api/3/universal_avatar/view/type/project/avatar/10413?size=medium\"}},\"description\":\"Implement a gRPC endpoint that generates presigned S3 URLs for all media files (images, MCAPs, point clouds) associated with a CAS event. This allows the frontend to securely display images and download files without exposing S3 credentials.\\n\\n### **Requirements**\\n\\n* Query `cas_event_media` table by `event_id`\\n\\n* For each media file, generate a presigned S3 URL using AWS SDK\\n\\n* Support configurable expiration time (default 1 hour)\\n\\n* Return media metadata along with presigned URLs:\\n\\n* Media ID\\n\\n* Media type (IMAGE, MCAP, POINT_CLOUD, VIDEO)\\n\\n* Name (e.g., FRONT_CENTER, LEFT_CAMERA)\\n\\n* Presigned URL (time-limited access)\\n\\n* Timestamp (when media was captured)\\n\\n* Handle errors gracefully if S3 bucket/key doesn't exist\\n\\n### **Technical Details**\\n\\n**Files to modify:**\\n\\n* `adp/services/vehicle_fe/proto/vehicle_fe_service.proto`\\n\\n* `simian/modules/hive/ota/db/write.sql`\\n\\n* `adp/services/vehicle_fe/vehicle_fe_server.go`\\n\\n**Proto messages:**\\n\\n* `GetCASEventMediaPresignedUrlsRequest` (event_id, expiration_seconds)\\n\\n* `GetCASEventMediaPresignedUrlsResponse` (media array)\\n\\n* `MediaWithPresignedUrl` (media_id, media_type, name, presigned_url, timestamp)\\n\\n**AWS S3 Integration:**\\n\\n```\\nimport \\\"github.com/aws/aws-sdk-go/service/s3\\\"\\n\\n// Generate presigned URL\\nreq, _ := s3Client.GetObjectRequest(&s3.GetObjectInput{\\n    Bucket: aws.String(media.S3Bucket),\\n    Key:    aws.String(media.S3Key),\\n})\\nurl, err := req.Presign(time.Duration(expirationSeconds) * time.Second)\\n```\\n\\n**Media types from database:**\\n\\n* `IMAGE` - Camera images (JPEG/PNG)\\n\\n* `MCAP` - ROS bag recordings\\n\\n* `POINT_CLOUD` - LiDAR data\\n\\n* `VIDEO` - Video clips\\n\\n### **Testing**\\n\\n```\\n# Get presigned URLs\\ngrpcurl -plaintext \\\\\\n  -d '{\\\"event_id\\\": \\\"00000199ef4e6788-fdda36cd\\\", \\\"expiration_seconds\\\": 3600}' \\\\\\n  localhost:10267 \\\\\\n  adp.services.vehicle_fe.proto.VehicleFe/GetCASEventMediaPresignedUrls\\n\\n# Test URL in browser\\ncurl -I \\\"<presigned_url_from_response>\\\"\\n# Should return 200 OK and image headers\\n```\\n\\n### **Dependencies**\\n\\n* `GetCASEvent` API (to get event details before fetching media)\\n\\n* Database table: `cas_event_media`\\n\\n* S3 bucket: `cas-events` (or configured bucket)\\n\\n* AWS credentials with S3 read access\\n\\n\",\"assignee\":{\"self\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/rest/api/3/user?accountId=712020%3A7aba54a1-9293-4ebe-89fe-0bf390f32a5b\",\"accountId\":\"712020:7aba54a1-9293-4ebe-89fe-0bf390f32a5b\",\"emailAddress\":\"avi.agarwal@applied.co\",\"avatarUrls\":{\"48x48\":\"https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/712020:7aba54a1-9293-4ebe-89fe-0bf390f32a5b/596b2fa3-c4a9-473b-8a24-ba57d7e1b911/48\",\"24x24\":\"https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/712020:7aba54a1-9293-4ebe-89fe-0bf390f32a5b/596b2fa3-c4a9-473b-8a24-ba57d7e1b911/24\",\"16x16\":\"https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/712020:7aba54a1-9293-4ebe-89fe-0bf390f32a5b/596b2fa3-c4a9-473b-8a24-ba57d7e1b911/16\",\"32x32\":\"https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/712020:7aba54a1-9293-4ebe-89fe-0bf390f32a5b/596b2fa3-c4a9-473b-8a24-ba57d7e1b911/32\"},\"displayName\":\"Avi Agarwal\",\"active\":true,\"timeZone\":\"America/Los_Angeles\",\"accountType\":\"atlassian\"},\"priority\":{\"self\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/rest/api/3/priority/2\",\"iconUrl\":\"https://appliedint-katana.atlassian.net/images/icons/priorities/high_new.svg\",\"name\":\"P1\",\"id\":\"2\"},\"status\":{\"self\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/rest/api/3/status/10005\",\"description\":\"\",\"iconUrl\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/\",\"name\":\"Complete\",\"id\":\"10005\",\"statusCategory\":{\"self\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/rest/api/3/statuscategory/3\",\"id\":3,\"key\":\"done\",\"colorName\":\"green\",\"name\":\"Done\"}}},\"webUrl\":\"https://appliedint-katana.atlassian.net/browse/KATA-894\"},{\"expand\":\"renderedFields,names,schema,operations,editmeta,changelog,versionedRepresentations\",\"id\":\"12498\",\"self\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/rest/api/3/issue/12498\",\"key\":\"KATA-892\",\"fields\":{\"summary\":\"GetCASEvent gRPC Call\",\"issuetype\":{\"self\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/rest/api/3/issuetype/10005\",\"id\":\"10005\",\"description\":\"A small, distinct piece of work.\",\"iconUrl\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/rest/api/2/universal_avatar/view/type/issuetype/avatar/10318?size=medium\",\"name\":\"Task\",\"subtask\":false,\"avatarId\":10318,\"hierarchyLevel\":0},\"created\":\"2025-10-17T14:50:33.377-0700\",\"project\":{\"self\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/rest/api/3/project/10001\",\"id\":\"10001\",\"key\":\"KATA\",\"name\":\"Katana\",\"projectTypeKey\":\"software\",\"simplified\":false,\"avatarUrls\":{\"48x48\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/rest/api/3/universal_avatar/view/type/project/avatar/10413\",\"24x24\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/rest/api/3/universal_avatar/view/type/project/avatar/10413?size=small\",\"16x16\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/rest/api/3/universal_avatar/view/type/project/avatar/10413?size=xsmall\",\"32x32\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/rest/api/3/universal_avatar/view/type/project/avatar/10413?size=medium\"}},\"description\":\"### **Description**\\n\\nImplement a gRPC endpoint to fetch complete details for a single CAS event by event ID. This API powers the event details page where safety officers can view all data about a specific collision avoidance event including full telemetry, detected objects, and media references.\\n\\n### **Requirements**\\n\\n* Query `cas_events` and `cas_event_media` tables by `event_id`\\n\\n* Return complete event details including:\\n\\n* Full event metadata\\n\\n* Complete risk level data (JSON)\\n\\n* Global state data (vehicle position, velocity)\\n\\n* Vehicle dynamics (speed, acceleration, steering angle)\\n\\n* System health data (CPU, GPU, memory usage)\\n\\n* Full detected objects array (all bounding boxes from perception)\\n\\n* Trigger objects with complete bounding box data\\n\\n* All media references (images, MCAPs, point clouds)\\n\\n* Review information (status, notes, reviewed by, timestamp)\\n\\n### **Technical Details**\\n\\n**Files to modify:**\\n\\n* `adp/services/vehicle_fe/proto/vehicle_fe_service.proto`\\n\\n* `simian/modules/hive/ota/db/write.sql`\\n\\n* `adp/services/vehicle_fe/vehicle_fe_server.go`\\n\\n**Proto messages:**\\n\\n* `GetCASEventRequest` (event_id)\\n\\n* `GetCASEventResponse` (full event details)\\n\\n* `CASEventDetail` (complete event data with all nested objects)\\n\\n**JSONB fields to parse:**\\n\\n* `risk_level_data`\\n\\n* `global_state_data`\\n\\n* `transmission_data`\\n\\n* `vehicle_dynamics_data`\\n\\n* `system_health_data`\\n\\n* `detected_objects_data`\\n\\n* `trigger_objects`\\n\\n\",\"assignee\":{\"self\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/rest/api/3/user?accountId=712020%3A7aba54a1-9293-4ebe-89fe-0bf390f32a5b\",\"accountId\":\"712020:7aba54a1-9293-4ebe-89fe-0bf390f32a5b\",\"emailAddress\":\"avi.agarwal@applied.co\",\"avatarUrls\":{\"48x48\":\"https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/712020:7aba54a1-9293-4ebe-89fe-0bf390f32a5b/596b2fa3-c4a9-473b-8a24-ba57d7e1b911/48\",\"24x24\":\"https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/712020:7aba54a1-9293-4ebe-89fe-0bf390f32a5b/596b2fa3-c4a9-473b-8a24-ba57d7e1b911/24\",\"16x16\":\"https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/712020:7aba54a1-9293-4ebe-89fe-0bf390f32a5b/596b2fa3-c4a9-473b-8a24-ba57d7e1b911/16\",\"32x32\":\"https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/712020:7aba54a1-9293-4ebe-89fe-0bf390f32a5b/596b2fa3-c4a9-473b-8a24-ba57d7e1b911/32\"},\"displayName\":\"Avi Agarwal\",\"active\":true,\"timeZone\":\"America/Los_Angeles\",\"accountType\":\"atlassian\"},\"priority\":{\"self\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/rest/api/3/priority/2\",\"iconUrl\":\"https://appliedint-katana.atlassian.net/images/icons/priorities/high_new.svg\",\"name\":\"P1\",\"id\":\"2\"},\"status\":{\"self\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/rest/api/3/status/10005\",\"description\":\"\",\"iconUrl\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/\",\"name\":\"Complete\",\"id\":\"10005\",\"statusCategory\":{\"self\":\"https://api.atlassian.com/ex/jira/eadd00c6-0d3f-4c89-99e3-ad95a0daaa51/rest/api/3/statuscategory/3\",\"id\":3,\"key\":\"done\",\"colorName\":\"green\",\"name\":\"Done\"}}},\"webUrl\":\"https://appliedint-katana.atlassian.net/browse/KATA-892\"}],\"webUrl\":\"https://appliedint-katana.atlassian.net/issues?jql=project%20%3D%20KATA%20AND%20text%20~%20%22MCAP%22%20AND%20text%20~%20%22ADP%22%20ORDER%20BY%20created%20DESC\",\"pageInfo\":{\"hasNextPage\":false,\"endCursor\":null}}}"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01AeQvEvhszVJhWytvQBSm5n","session_id":"e608aebc-1e8f-4a54-bfcc-c9052cb98c4e","uuid":"280cc6a6-212f-4dfd-9715-0eaa04bb0f43","timestamp":"2026-06-01T17:05:28.592Z","subagent_type":"general-purpose","task_description":"Research ROSbag/MCAP format for ADP pipeline"}
